68
00:06:18,844 --> 00:06:20,400
Hello, Anti-abduction Office.

69
00:06:20,744 --> 00:06:22,711
Yan Lei, Whiteboard
is a gambling addict.

70
00:06:22,888 --> 00:06:24,569
Investigate the entertainment cities

71
00:06:24,570 --> 00:06:26,070
