775
00:39:28,955 --> 00:39:30,200
Don't you know the rules?

776
00:39:30,800 --> 00:39:31,640
Xie.

777
00:39:32,480 --> 00:39:34,150
Do you not believe in us?

778
00:39:34,555 --> 00:39:35,888
Everyone in the underworld

779
00:39:35,888 --> 00:39:36,920
